"{\"uid\": \"scmp.com-news-hong-kong-hong-kong-economy-article-3274830-hong-kongs-cathay-records-15-rise-passenger-traffic-july-amid-olympics-travel-demand\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Hong Kong flag carrier Cathay Pacific Airways has recorded a 15 per cent year-on-year increase in the passenger traffic, exceeding 2 million in July, amid robust demand from those travelling to Paris for the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 9, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9976776577713313, \"rank\": 0.001062069926828201, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}, {\"begin\": 23, \"end\": 29, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cathay\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.213285289045566e-15, \"text\": \"Cathay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cathay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cathay\"}, {\"begin\": 30, \"end\": 37, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Ocean\", \"score\": 0.9905648602372575, \"rank\": 0.009372820303935407, \"text\": \"Pacific\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Ocean\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pacific_Ocean\"}, {\"begin\": 194, \"end\": 199, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999973091425823, \"rank\": 2.690864597327566e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"year\", \"from\": 81, \"to\": 85}, {\"ngram\": \"the passenger traffic\", \"from\": 98, \"to\": 119}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 144, \"to\": 148}, {\"ngram\": \"robust demand\", \"from\": 155, \"to\": 168}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 204, \"to\": 221}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The airline said on Friday that July was a \\\"milestone month\\\" with 2,008,225 passengers, the first time the airline hit more than 2 million in a single month since the pandemic.\", \"from\": 224, \"to\": 400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The airline\", \"from\": 224, \"to\": 235}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 250}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 260}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"milestone month\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 283}, {\"ngram\": \"2,008,225 passengers\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 310}, {\"ngram\": \"the airline\", \"from\": 327, \"to\": 338}, {\"ngram\": \"a single month\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"the pandemic\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lavinia Lau Hoi-zee, Cathay's chief customer and commercial officer, said such robust demand was driven by the increased popularity of long-haul flights to and from Hong Kong in the first half of the month, among students and those visiting friends and relatives.\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 665, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 402, \"end\": 409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lavinia\", \"score\": 0.9999999978255119, \"rank\": 1.9951844080104616e-09, \"text\": \"Lavinia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lavinia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lavinia\"}, {\"begin\": 410, \"end\": 413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Lau\", \"score\": 0.9876478528265241, \"rank\": 0.012499742145838941, \"text\": \"Lau\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Lau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Lau\"}, {\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cathay\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.213285289045566e-15, \"text\": \"Cathay\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cathay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cathay\"}, {\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"score\": 0.9976776577713313, \"rank\": 0.001062069926828201, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"such robust demand\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 494}, {\"ngram\": \"the increased popularity\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 533}, {\"ngram\": \"long-haul flights\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 554}, {\"ngram\": \"the first half\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 594}, {\"ngram\": \"the month\", \"from\": 598, \"to\": 607}, {\"ngram\": \"students\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 623}, {\"ngram\": \"those visiting friends\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 650}, {\"ngram\": \"relatives\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In addition, we saw strong demand for flights to Paris due to the Olympic Games, and we were delighted to carry a significant number of athletes and spectators to attend this momentous sporting occasion,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 882, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 717, \"end\": 722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999973091425823, \"rank\": 2.690864597327566e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 671, \"to\": 679}, {\"ngram\": \"strong demand\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 701}, {\"ngram\": \"flights\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant number\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 812}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 827}, {\"ngram\": \"this momentous sporting occasion\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lau also highlighted the increase in travel to popular short-haul destinations in Japan and Southeast Asia during the latter half of July.\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 1022, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 884